    • Field Detail

      • ALTERNATIVE_HASHING

        static final boolean ALTERNATIVE_HASHING
        Enable alternative hashing of String keys?

        Unlike the other hash map implementations we do not implement a threshold for regulating whether alternative hashing is used for String keys. Alternative hashing is either enabled for all instances or disabled for all instances.
